def find_min(nums):
    if not nums:
        return -1
    left, right = 0, len(nums) - 1
    while left < right:
        mid = left + (right - left) // 2
        if nums[mid] < nums[right]:    # right side is sorted, move search to unsorted side
            right = mid
        elif nums[mid] > nums[right]:  # left side is sorted, move search to unsorted side
            left = mid + 1
        else:   # we cannot know which side is sorted, continue with binary search
            right -= 1
    return nums[left]
